### Complexhibit API - HTTP Tests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Health Check - Root Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### PERSONAS (Persons)
### ============================================

### Get all persons
GET {{baseUrl}}/all_personas
Accept: application/json

### Count actants
GET {{baseUrl}}/count_actants
Accept: application/json

### Get person by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/get_persona/human%20actant/abc123
Accept: application/json

### Create new person
POST {{baseUrl}}/post_persona
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pablo Picasso",
  "type": "Individual",
  "country": "Spain",
  "birth_date": "25/10/1881",
  "death_date": "08/04/1973",
  "activity": ["Painter", "Sculptor"],
  "gender": "Male"
}

